show.description: In a world ruled by power hungry wolf clans, Sara was never meant to lead. But when betrayal shatters her family and love challenges her destiny, she must fight to reclaim what's rightfully hers. This is the epic journey of how she rose from the shadows to become the true Alpha Queen. Watch Now.
